dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.serviceneeds

Interface IDiagnosticValueNeeds

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDiagnosticCapabilityElement, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable, IServiceNeeds

    public interface IDiagnosticValueNeeds
extends IEntity, IDiagnosticCapabilityElement
    IDiagnosticValueNeeds: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Specifies the general needs on the configuration of the Diagnostic Communication Manager (DCM) which are not related to a particular item (e.g. a PID). The main use case is the mapping of service ports to the DCM which are not related to a particular item. In the case of using a sender receiver communicated value, the related value shall be taken via assignedData in the role "signalBasedDiagnostics". In case of using a client/server communicated value, the related value shall be communicated via the port referenced by asssignedPort. The details of this communication (e.g. appropriate naming conventions) are specified in the related software specifications (SWS).

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
